Configuration files for my main desktop (arch linux)

Includes:
	- alacritty | terminal emulator
	- helix | text editor / IDE
	- fish | shell
	- wireplumber | audio
	- zellij | terminal workspaces
	- hypr | window manager and its utilities
	- hyprpanel | status bar
	- aerc | email client

Install via

sh -c "$(curl -fsLS get.chezmoi.io)" -- init --apply iraizo
